@startuml
title analysis.build_dataset - Dataset construction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

component "build_dataset.py\npython -m analysis.build_dataset" as ds
database "results_normalized/\nnormalized JSONL" as norm
database "analysis_out/" as out
file "dataset_long.csv" as long
file "dataset_wide_<component_type>.csv" as wide

norm --> ds : read normalized rows
ds --> long : append long-form rows\n(project, component, metric, tool, value,...)
ds --> wide : pivot to wide format\n(one row per component)

ds --> out : write supporting artifacts\n(e.g. metadata summaries)

note right of ds
Makefile target: dataset
Key arg:
--wide-component-type file
end note

@enduml
